v",{"^var":"trust_xin","ci":-1},2,{"f()":"adjust_trust"},"pop","/ev","\n","#","^state:fear_xin+5","/#",{"->":".^.^.choose_action"},null],"talk_zhiyong":["#","^speaker:zhiyong","/#","ev",{"f()":"tick_round"},"pop","/ev","\n","^Zhiyong clicks his tongue. \"Tch. What's the holdup. If we were going to break out we'd have done it already. If we're going to lie around, then keep lying around.\" His leg pauses, then resumes its jiggling.","\n","ev",{"^var":"trust_zhiyong","ci":-1},3,{"f()":"adjust_trust"},"pop","/ev","\n","#","^state:trust_zhiyong+3","/#",{"->":".^.^.choose_action"},null],"talk_zhangyi":["#","^speaker:zhangyi","/#","ev",{"f()":"tick_round"},"pop","/ev","\n","^Zhangyi pushes up the bridge of nonexistent glasses. \"I'm inclined to first list out everything we know for certain... wait. That sound just now — was it from upstairs?\"","\n","ev",{"^var":"trust_zhangyi","ci":-1},3,{"f()":"adjust_trust"},"pop","/ev","\n","ev",{"VAR?":"aw_unease"},{"f()":"reach_awareness"},"pop","/ev","\n","#","^state:trust_zhangyi+3","/#",{"->":".^.^.choose_action"},null],"idle_wait":["ev",{"f()":"tick_round"},"pop","/ev","\n","^The room goes quiet again. Zhiyong shifts position and keeps jiggling. The searchlight sweeps across the iron sheet outside; the bright stripe crawls across the wall.","\n",{"->":".^.^.choose_action"},null]}],"scene_noodle_contest":[["#","^scene:dorm_302","/#","#","^speaker:yanbo","/#","ev",true,"/ev",{"VAR=":"noodle_done","re":true},"ev",{"f()":"tick_round"},"pop","/ev","\n","^Yanbo sees it first. The last cup of pickled-cabbage instant noodles, wedged at the back of the snack shelf — the very last cup of lockdown day seven. He reaches in and clutches it to his chest.","\n","^\"This is mine,\" he says, completely serious.","\n","^Zhiyong clicks his tongue. \"Come on, who was the one who said he wasn't hungry just now?\"","\n","^Zhangyi straightens. \"I'm inclined to settle this by drawing lots.\"","\n","^Xin, quietly: \"What about... we split it four ways and cook it together? I mean, just in case...\"","\n","ev","str","^Side with drawing lots","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},"ev","str","^Side with sharing","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":20},"ev","str","^Let Yanbo have it","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-2","flg":20},{"c-0":["\n","ev",{"^var":"trust_zhangyi","ci":-1},5,{"f()":"adjust_trust"},"pop","/ev","\n","^The lot falls to Zhangyi. Yanbo grumbles and surrenders the noodles, but Zhangyi pushes them back into the pot. \"Four-way split.\"","\n",{"->":".^.^.g-0"},{"#f":5}],"c-1":["\n","ev",{"^var":"trust_xin","ci":-1},5,{"f()":"adjust_trust"},"pop","/ev","\n","^Xin exhales. Zhiyong, cursing under his breath, takes over the cooking.","\n",{"->":".^.^.g-0"},{"#f":5}],"c-2":["\n","ev",{"^var":"fear_xin","ci":-1},{"^var":"status_xin","ci":-1},5,{"f()":"adjust_fear"},"pop","/ev","\n","^Yanbo carries the noodles smugly to his desk. Xin stares at the empty pot, says nothing.","\n",{"->":".^.^.g-0"},{"#f":5}],"g-0":["^The water boils. Steam rises and merges with the dim yellow of the fluorescent light.","\n","ev",{"f()":"advance_foreshadow"},"pop","/ev","\n","ev",{"VAR?":"aw_smell"},{"f()":"reach_awareness"},"pop","/ev","\n",["ev",{"VAR?":"foreshadow"},{"VAR?":"fs_l1"},"?","/ev",{"->":".^.b","c":true},{"b":["\n","^A strange sweet-rotten note drifts up through the steam — must be the seasoning packet getting damp.","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.16"},null]}],["ev",{"VAR?":"foreshadow"},{"VAR?":"fs_l2"},"?","/ev",{"->":".^.b","c":true},{"b":["\n","^The corridor light at the far end dips by a fraction, as if for a single beat, then steadies.","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.16"},null]}],["ev",{"VAR?":"foreshadow"},{"VAR?":"fs_l3"},"?","/ev",{"->":".^.b","c":true},{"b":["\n","^Rummaging in the shelf, your fingers brush a slip of paper that wasn't there before. Scrawled across it: \"Don't open the door.\"","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.16"},null]}],"nop","\n",{"->":"scene_dorm_evening"},null]}],null],"scene_midnight_knock":[["#","^scene:dorm_302","/#","#","^sfx:knock_3x","/#","ev",{"f()":"tick_round"},"pop","/ev","\n","ev",{"VAR?":"aw_knock1"},{"f()":"reach_awareness"},"pop","/ev","\n","^At some point — none of you noticed when — everyone has stopped moving.","\n","^From outside the door, three knocks. Even, steady. Knock — knock — knock.","\n","^Then the pause.","\n","^The blood drains from Xin's face; he presses against the wall. Zhiyong stands up, but does not move. Zhangyi, low: \"Wait —\"","\n","ev","str","^Call out: \"Who's there?\"","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},"ev","str","^Hold your breath and listen","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":20},"ev","str","^Send Zhiyong to check","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-2","flg":20},{"c-0":["\n","ev",{"^var":"fear_xin","ci":-1},{"^var":"status_xin","ci":-1},10,{"f()":"adjust_fear"},"pop","/ev","\n","#","^state:fear_xin+10","/#","^Your voice rings off the walls. From the other side of the door, no answer.","\n",{"->":".^.^.g-0"},{"#f":5}],"c-1":["\n","ev",60,{"f()":"roll_skill"},"/ev",{"temp=":"heard"},"\n","ev",{"VAR?":"heard"},"/ev",[{"->":".^.b","c":true},{"b":["\n","^There is breathing on the other side — slow, wet, pulsing in a rhythm that does not belong to anything alive. ","#","^debug:listen_pass","/#","\n","ev",{"VAR?":"aw_outside"},{"f()":"reach_awareness"},"pop","/ev","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.12"},null]}],[{"->":".^.b"},{"b":["\n","^On the other side, absolute silence. A silence too clean to be real. ","#","^debug:listen_fail","/#","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.12"},null]}],"nop","\n",{"->":".^.^.g-0"},{"#f":5}],"c-2":["\n","^Zhiyong scoffs. \"Fine, I'll look.\" He walks to the door, presses his ear against it — and then, immediately, steps back. He says nothing.","\n","ev",{"^var":"fear_zhiyong","ci":-1},{"^var":"status_zhiyong","ci":-1},8,{"f()":"adjust_fear"},"pop","/ev","\n","#","^state:fear_zhiyong+8","/#",{"->":".^.^.g-0"},{"#f":5}],"g-0":["^Three more knocks. Knock — knock — knock.","\n","ev",{"VAR?":"aw_knock2"},{"f()":"reach_awareness"},"pop","/ev","\n","ev",{"f()":"advance_foreshadow"},"pop","/ev","\n","^This time, after the third knock, no fourth comes. But the breathing on the other side does not move away.","\n","ev","str","^Open the door","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-3","flg":20},"ev","str","^Don't open. Back away.","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-4","flg":20},"ev","str","^Try to call the dorm-mom","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-5","flg":20},{"c-3":["^ ",{"->":"scene_cut_in.open_door"},"\n",{"#f":5}],"c-4":["^ ",{"->":"scene_cut_in.keep_door_closed"},"\n",{"#f":5}],"c-5":["^ ",{"->":"scene_cut_in.call_manager_fail"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}]}],null],"scene_cut_in":["#","^act:1","/#","#","^scene:dorm_302","/#","#","^bgm:cut_in_horror","/#",{"->":".^.default_cut_in"},{"default_cut_in":["^The four of you freeze in place.","\n",{"->":".^.^.finale"},null],"open_door":["^You slowly turn the handle.","\n","^The door cracks open. The corridor's motion-sensor lights are flickering. Yellow caution tape lies all across the floor, much of it torn loose, soaking in a dark red viscous liquid.","\n","^There is no one at the door. But on the door frame — a hand, gripping it from the outside. The fingernails are split. The skin is pale.","\n",{"->":".^.^.finale"},null],"keep_door_closed":["^Together you back into the corner.","\n","^The breathing on the other side is still there. And then, slowly — slowly — the door handle begins to turn. Not turned by anyone. Turning on its own.","\n",{"->":".^.^.finale"},null],"call_manager_fail":["^Xin dials. No signal. Zhangyi checks his own phone. \"Mine too. No signal.\"","\n","^On the other side of the door, a long scrape begins to drag down the door panel from top to bottom — like a fingernail.","\n",{"->":".^.^.finale"},null],"finale":["ev",{"VAR?":"awareness"},{"VAR?":"aw_outside"},"?","/ev",[{"->":".^.b","c":true},{"b":["\n","^The breathing on the other side — it was not a trick of the mind, not imagination.","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.6"},null]}],"nop","\n","ev",{"VAR?":"awareness"},{"VAR?":"aw_smell"},"?","/ev",[{"->":".^.b","c":true},{"b":["\n"